Boolean() constructor can be used for explicit boolean conversion.

conversion rule:(same rule for explicit as well as implicit conversion)
undefined to false
null to false
empty string to false
"123" to true
"abc" to true
0 to false
-0 to false
NaN to false
Infinity to true
123 to true
array to true
object to true

